<li>Words cannot express how saddened I am to hear of your loss.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace as you grieve.</li>
<li>May your family find solace in the love you shared.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, thinking of you all.</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
